# Implementation Plan - JEF HRIS Modernization & Premium Visual Redesign

We will completely transform the e-Attendance e-Productivity portal into a spectacular, high-fidelity human capital dashboard matching the visuals of high-end SaaS tools (with modern glassmorphism UI, vibrant colors, sub-pixel retina-ready layout spacing, responsive tables, and live data insights).

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Key Enhancements Proposed**:
> 1. **Sidebar Menu Modernization**: Modernizing the sidebar names to be ultra-premium, clean, and concise (Dashboard, Talents, Approvals, Attendance, Leaves, Structure, Tasks, Holidays, Settings).
> 2. **Landing Page Apps Feature Banner**: We are adding a premium welcome banner and **HRIS Features Showcase Grid** at the top of the main Dashboard page. This turns the dashboard into a gorgeous "Landing Hub" with interactive shortcut widgets for each of e-Attendance's features.
> 3. **Simplified, Responsive Datatable Layout**: Reducing columns in the admin tasks table from 9 to 6 (removing minor columns like Category, Description, and Attachment from the grid view).
> 4. **Bento Details View Modal**: Creating an in-app glassmorphic details modal (`#modalViewTaskAdmin`) to present the simplified task elements in a beautiful, structured display with one-click Drive attachment previewing.
> 5. **Admin Task Analytics Insights**: Injecting a dynamic statistical banner at the top of the Admin Task manager page to display live productivity statistics.

